snippet.title: Sonic & Blaze SAGE 2022 Preview 1 - Blue Coast
snippet.description:
SAGE is coming up soon so I'm uploading new updated versions of completed stages to use for the booth.

This is Blue Coast Act 1 but S-Ranked because I figured I should show that it actually exists instead of getting another C/D rank lol

Some more minor stuff hidden here but for the most part what you see here is what you'll get in August when the SAGE demo drops.

download link: https://sonicfangameshq.com/forums/showcase/sonic-blaze-sage-2022-edition.1515/
